<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="speak-vt">speak <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /spiːk/    美 /spiːk/  </p>
<p>(spoke, spoken)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[不用于进行时] 说 (语言)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>can speak</strong> several languages. 
他会讲好几种语言。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>说 (话)；表达：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>speak / tell the truth 
说实话</p></div>

<p>注: speaking常与某些副词连用，作插入语。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>strictly / roughly / generally speaking 
严格/大体/一般说来</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="speak-for">speak for</h3>
<p>1.<strong>代表…讲话 / 发言</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="speak-highly-of">speak highly of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>赞扬：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>World media spoke highly of China’s achievements in reform. 
世界各国媒体高度评价中国改革所取得的成就。</p></div>

<h3 id="speak-of">speak of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>谈到；提及：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He spoke of the French and their “habit of standing in a queue”. 
他谈到了法国人以及他们排队的习惯。</p></div>

<h3 id="speak-out-up">speak out / up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>清楚响亮地说；大胆地说：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Speak out — we can’t hear you. 
大声说，我们听不见你说话。</p></div></div>